{"tid":1395971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈推薦一套漫畫「約定的夢幻島」（所有藍絲黃絲都應該看）","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T05:16:14.000Z","uid":293048,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e323ad9773db4c57bfd70160eb7fe5eaa20e455","tid":1395971,"uid":293048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:37:43.000Z","msg":"這故事發生在孤兒院，3個主角都在這孤兒院長大，他們一直很安分守己，大家和平相處，也很愛孤兒院。但慢慢開始發覺孤兒院很不尋常，原本一直應該好好照顧他們的褓母原來有任務在身，背後的操控者很不簡單。他們知道殘酷一天遲早會到來，大家也掙扎過要不要逃離，但最後知道不做什麼就改變不了，為了生存，也希望同時也救出其他孤兒，大家也合作起來一起逃離孤兒院，也不得不做很多孤兒院不許做的事。之後發覺出面世界也是黑暗，而且跟自己孤兒院有千絲萬縷的關係，如果不小心，隨時會像被捉回來，他們為了生存就只好繼續迎難而上......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B4%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A2%E5%B9%BB%E5%B3%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%25A2%25E5%25B9%25BB%25E5%25B3%25B6&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=f80431fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B4%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A2%E5%B9%BB%E5%B3%B6</a>"},{"pid":"9d4af0722d28fc7e813c64c32fa3ee42c26f13d4","tid":1395971,"uid":293048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:53:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"adba1ded199cd9606dec08062dde4f9812130a7f","tid":1395971,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:55:07.000Z","msg":"睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推薦"},{"pid":"e353f12c78fae28d753fe77f800d7a67613c6142","tid":1395971,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:56:33.000Z","msg":"有睇 天才兒童FF故<br />\n同食肉議題有啲關係 幾有意思<br />\n但唔明點解強烈推薦"},{"pid":"c227cd894008dc2f1b11e2ffe2338af4216eff93","tid":1395971,"uid":293048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"